===At Spawn===

This method requires the use of a weapon that attacks at a rate of 3 ticks, such as a [[Craw's bow]] or [[Magic shortbow]] on rapid.
*By standing 8 tiles west of Venenatis' regular spawn (tile 1 in the image), and clicking attack 1 tick after Venenatis spawns, it will be automatically safespotted.
*After 4 attacks from a Craw's bow, you can then run south-east exactly 4 tiles from where you are standing (to tile 2 in the image) and immediately continue attacking.
*Now you are free to move 1 more tile east into single-way combat, and even further east and south to the full attack range of your weapon. As long as you don't miss any combat ticks during movement, Venenatis will not attack you.
*If Venenatis spawns offset from its usual spawn, you can run outside of its aggression range to force it to return to its spawn and try again.
